description: Experience luxury living in this one-of-a-kind,rarely available K-Unit residence on the 10th floor at 50 Liberty Drive with direct water views.This premier front-facing stunning corner unit offers 10.5ft ceilings with waterfront views of Boston Harbor Waterfront through expansive floor-to-ceiling windows in every room creating breathtaking ambiance.The open floor plan showcases,large waterfall island with custom high-gloss white lacquer cabinetry,Sub-Zero refrigerator,wine chiller,Miele dishwasher,Wolf stovetop&wall oven.Spacious living/dining flows seamlessly to a large private terrace,providing panoramic views of the Harbor perfect for relaxation.Primary bedroom features a gorgeous en-suite bathroom,2-custom walk-in closets.2nd bedroom features en-suite bathroom&2 closets.Plus Den/guest room,2 garage parking spaces&storage.Amenities include 24 hour concierge/doorman,fitness center,boardroom,club room with waterfront terrace.Located near Seaports finest restaurants,cafes,shops,Airport
